      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING QUIZ (7) placed three back at this track then out of the placings last couple but moves to box 7 this time where he has performed well. Has the ability and expected to go close. KRAKEN HUGGIE (3) pinged the lids last start from an awkward draw and led throughout to score (22.27) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can measure up again. AUSSIE WAGYU (5) jumped from out wide and had a clear run, crossing to the lead and holding on for a placing when second (22.27) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Leading player again. PAW YAZ (2) placed last time at this track and distance - worth some thought.",
